{"tid":1704661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係波鞋撚，呢張文宣炒咗車","createTime":"2019-11-10T18:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T19:54:12.000Z","uid":159172,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"340420c413a05a381cfa184bc93a688e5fae4ae4","tid":1704661,"uid":159172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mEiSnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mEiSnE.jpg&h=6bd3c253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果睇下鞋底紋理同形狀<br />\n我斷定係一對Ultra boost相信大家都會同意。<br />\n<br />\n歷代出嘅ultra Boost 1.0去到4.0，<br />\n每一代<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>黑色</strong></span>鞋面嘅話，鞋底都<span style=\"font-size: large;\">必然係黑色</span><br />\n<br />\n印像中出過有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>[black]黑色鞋面[/black]</strong></span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>加白色鞋底</em></span></strong>嘅。以我認知我得三款<br />\n<br />\n1: Hybeast X UltraBoost 1.0 Uncaged<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZtr1gF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZtr1gF.jpg&h=a0853930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. Undefeated Ultra boost 4.0<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/diM5xor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdiM5xor.jpg&h=366928e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. UltraBoost 4.0 &ldquo;Orca&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07t0mgR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07t0mgR.jpg&h=805c7d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 萬幾銀一對正常人唔係會捨着。仲要係白色鞋踭唔會係全黑。<br />\n2.鞋頭會有一項好大嘅白色&quot;UNDEFEATED&quot;字樣。<br />\n3. Orca 嘅三間鞋框係白色唔會係全黑色<br />\n<br />\n所以我判斷可能性得兩個：<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周同學對嘢一係老翻，一係入咗對Orca就自訂剪框/噴框。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">換言之呢對嘢唔係市面上咁容易買到，要做假嘅機會好低。對鞋都相信係啱啱新落地無耐，所以離遠睇似係白色都好正常。</span><br />\n<br />\n點都好做偵探嘅時間已經過啦，大家早啲瞓聽日再打過啦。<br />\n<br />\n就算張圖點樣都好。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">周同學唔係失足避催淚彈跌落去。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢係被政權推下去。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仆個街佢同我同齡，你班黑警一定要同我冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，報仇。</span>"},{"pid":"2937bf592d83916dcfeed6e54069487cb441ef41","tid":1704661,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b913337f2ee11e68ad9a809d05aa20c98c0d77fa","tid":1704661,"uid":232360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"乜鳩遠睇似白色 鞋底黑色遠睇白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbc15721a04d9173ab5a202bfa1882cbbddf150","tid":1704661,"uid":64830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T19:54:12.000Z","msg":"拉 第一個po開完上唔到熱門又開過？<br />\n放完幾張圖都唔知up乜鳩"}]}